  "id": "api/core/Input",
  "title": "Input",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L815-L816\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L815-L816\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/Input\", \"name\": \"Input\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"input\">Input<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Input#input\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    \n    \n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  \n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>Option</th><th>Description</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/Input#bindingPropertyName\">\n          <code>bindingPropertyName</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td><p>Decorator that marks a class field as an input property and supplies configuration metadata.\nDeclares a data-bound input property, which Angular automatically updates\nduring change detection.</p>\n</td>\n    </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">Options<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Input#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <a id=\"bindingPropertyName\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead><tr><th>\n      <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n        <h3 id=\"bindingpropertyname\">bindingPropertyName<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Input#bindingpropertyname\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n        <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L729-L773\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L729-L773\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p>Decorator that marks a class field as an input property and supplies configuration metadata.\nDeclares a data-bound input property, which Angular automatically updates\nduring change detection.</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n          bindingPropertyName: string\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p>You can supply an optional name to use in templates when the\ncomponent is instantiated, that maps to the\nname of the bound property. By default, the original\nname of the bound property is used for input binding.</p>\n<p>The following example creates a component with two input properties,\none of which is given a special binding name.</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'bank-account',\n  <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `\n    Bank Name: {{bankName}}\n    Account Id: {{id}}\n  `\n})\nclass BankAccount {\n  // This property is bound using its original name.\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() bankName: string;\n  // this property value is bound to <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> different property name\n  // when this component is instantiated in <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> template.\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>('account-id') id: string;\n\n  // this property is not bound, and is not automatically updated by Angular\n  normalizedBankName: string;\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `\n    &#x3C;bank-account bankName=\"RBC\" account-id=\"4747\">&#x3C;/bank-account>\n  `\n})\n\nclass App {}\n</code-example>\n\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgClass\n - api/common/NgComponentOutlet\n - api/common/NgForOf\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/common/NgPlural\n - api/common/NgStyle\n - api/common/NgSwitch\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgTemplateOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/core/ContentChild\n - api/core/ContentChildren\n - api/core/OnChanges\n - api/core/ViewChild\n - api/core/ViewChildren\n - api/forms/EmailValidator\n - api/forms/FormArrayName\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormGroupDirective\n - api/forms/FormGroupName\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\n - api/forms/MinLengthValidator\n - api/forms/NgForm\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/NgModelGroup\n - api/forms/NgSelectOption\n - api/forms/PatternValidator\n - api/forms/RadioControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator\n - api/forms/SelectControlValueAccessor\n - api/forms/SelectMultipleControlValueAccessor\n - api/router/RouterLink\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - api/upgrade/UpgradeAdapter\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - api/upgrade/static/downgradeComponent\n - guide/aot-compiler\n - guide/attribute-directives\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/dependency-injection-in-action\n - guide/dynamic-component-loader\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/elements\n - guide/form-validation\n - guide/glossary\n - guide/hierarchical-dependency-injection\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/structural-directives\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n - guide/upgrade-performance\n - tutorial/toh-pt3\n - tutorial/toh-pt6\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#template\n - api/core/Input#bindingPropertyName\n - api/core/Input#bindingpropertyname\n - api/core/Input#input\n - api/core/Input#options\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L729-L773\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L815-L816\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L729-L773\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L815-L816\n-->"
